OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of an
OL,6,Fisolated shower or thunderstorm during
OL,7,Fthe evening, otherwise a fine and dry
OL,8,Fnight. Rather warm for many eastern
OL,9,Fareas, although feeling slightly
OL,10,Ffresher in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry, mostly sunny day,
OL,13,Fperhaps the chance for some rain or
OL,14,Fshowers, possibly thundery in the
OL,15,Fsouth for a time. Feeling fresher
OL,16,Finland, but warmer at the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
